item.title: CVE-2022-1523|2024-09-16T20:13:11.760Z -- fuji%20electric -- d300win
item.description: Fuji Electric D300win prior to version 3.7.1.17 is vulnerable to a write-what-where condition, which could allow an attacker to overwrite program memory to manipulate the flow of information.
